Third-party assets (not covered by the MIT license above)

The project bundles a two-track background playlist:
1) Vladimir_Putin_-_Molodec_politik_lider_i_borec_72438381.mp3 — «Молодец, политик,
   лидер и борец» (Владимир Путин), listing URL: https://rus.hitmotop.com/song/72438381
2) Slava_KPSS_Pyrokinesis_-_RKN_74532024.mp3 — «РКН» (Слава КПСС, Pyrokinesis),
   listing URL: https://rus.hitmotop.com/song/74532024

These tracks were included by the project authors on their own initiative, without
a separate agreement with the rights holders; attribution is provided in good faith.
Copyright and related rights remain with the authors and/or their licensees. The
files are bundled for use as in-game soundtrack assets; redistribution of the audio
may require separate permission from the rights holders.

---

Configuration files

Optional file dev-secrets.js (see dev-secrets.example.js) may override the
expected SHA-256 hash for the developer cheat menu. Do not commit private
hashes or passwords to public repositories if you intend to keep them secret.
